{"tid":2002350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲差6萬！民主派眾籌制衡李慧琼！索取議會憲制運作資深大律師獨立法律意見","createTime":"2020-05-05T06:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T03:00:21.000Z","uid":210495,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a794a2bd509522ecca0bd9d280edc3f87ecd884d","tid":2002350,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:46:35.000Z","msg":"眾籌連結：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><a href=\"https://qrgo.page.link/HQaJU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqrgo.page.link%2FHQaJU&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=5b212d2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qrgo.page.link/HQaJU</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/95329468_10157915256160733_3530257573062115328_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_oc=AQmyL3wan3hyhLy3M0A_gUAYe4FzQEA-Ip9hnt_Eti2i8OoatO4rwlxum0coiM-QNO0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=bf7b8f3ed05fa86db937173210f210a6&amp;oe=5ED7A073\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F95329468_10157915256160733_3530257573062115328_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_oc%3DAQmyL3wan3hyhLy3M0A_gUAYe4FzQEA-Ip9hnt_Eti2i8OoatO4rwlxum0coiM-QNO0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dbf7b8f3ed05fa86db937173210f210a6%26oe%3D5ED7A073&h=63603ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會內務委員會主席選舉僵持，過去數月相繼遭林鄭月娥、以至港澳辦及中聯辦口誅筆伐。行政干預立法、一國踐踏兩制，西環霸權赤裸人前！<br />\n<br />\n西環吹哨下，梁君彥火速以公帑外聘資深大律師，徹底否定立法會內部法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼將利用這個所謂「法律基礎」，在5月8日下午召開會議自我裁決，僭建權力。這份法律意見其實也矛盾處處，當中更坦言這種看法可能造成主席濫權，我們擔心這份法律意見一旦獲接納，議會傳統及制度將會崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌目的：<br />\n為了回應這份法律意見，民主派立法會議員集體聘請熟悉議會及憲制運作的資深大律師，目標於5月8日內會開會前，索取到權威的獨立法律意見，以補充及平衡這份法律意見的缺失。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌金額﹕<br />\n外聘大律師費用大約35萬港元，民主派繼《禁蒙面法》後再度眾籌，希望集市民之力守住議會。22名民主派議員會先集資11萬元，餘下款項向所有香港人募捐，眾籌目標為26.4萬港元（包括24萬港元和眾籌平台收取約10%即約2.4萬元手續費）。"},{"pid":"592a6c515ab0de3b0e199ccdc0305a4651a1b962","tid":2002350,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:48:17.000Z","msg":"tuiiiiiiiiiiiii"},{"pid":"e18a4d3fd7f86a68a7b70706a4b70939eb659d71","tid":2002350,"uid":5378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"外聘大律師唔係又李柱銘 余苦薇 av仁下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54456a01c1e6d4d512f4736e3f7826f47a74f81e","tid":2002350,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:50:37.000Z","msg":"Margaret Ng? &nbsp;唔知"},{"pid":"36fe163ffa17864ba8c98216bece7855f2a78c93","tid":2002350,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:52:05.000Z","msg":"做足所有野"},{"pid":"fefb27f65a6b2daa6c3089790e9f48347ccd3a00","tid":2002350,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e18a4d3fd7f86a68a7b70706a4b70939eb659d71","tid":2002350,"uid":5378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"外聘大律師唔係又李柱銘 余苦薇 av仁下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"應該係獨立意見，即係同泛民冇關係既大律師。"},{"pid":"bc467d59054c8b1c485818ac6c48f7da36066d23","tid":2002350,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fefb27f65a6b2daa6c3089790e9f48347ccd3a00","tid":2002350,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e18a4d3fd7f86a68a7b70706a4b70939eb659d71","tid":2002350,"uid":5378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"外聘大律師唔係又李柱銘 余苦薇 av仁下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"應該係獨立意見，即係同泛民冇關係既大律師。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgm